info.name: Queen Tumblr Logo
info.description: It replaces the tumblr logo with a white logo of the band Queen on your dashboard.
info.additionalInfo:
Make sure you have Stylish installed first. If you don't, you can find it here (for Chrome): https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/fjnbnpbmkenffdnngjfgmeleoegfcffe

If you have any questions or you're having a problem with it, contact me on my tumblr:
london-dreams.tumblr.com
